25|$|On August 28, 2017, King marched with <b>Al</b> <b>Sharpton</b> in Washington D.C. for the Ministers March for Justice leading over 3,000 {{ministers to}} protest the {{policies}} of President Donald J. Trump. King was under major controversy when he agreed to meet with Trump in January 2017.|$|E
