25|$|In June 2005, Sharpton {{signed a}} {{contract}} with Matrix Media to produce and host a live two-hour daily talk program, but it never aired. In November 2005, Sharpton signed with Radio One to host a daily national talk radio program, which began airing on January 30, 2006, entitled Keepin It Real with <b>Al</b> <b>Sharpton.</b>|$|E
